            <p>
                <strong>Using NTP + HTTP Date together</strong> is best:
            </p>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>NTP:</strong> Sync my computer to standard time (baseline accuracy)</li>
                <li><strong>SyncTime:</strong> Identify target server's time for fine-tuning</li>
            </ol>
            <p>
                This combination provides the highest success rate!
            </p>
        </div>

